    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This *+2 striking longspear* was crafted by a renowned monster hunter, who designed the prototype from the bones and scales of a diabolic dragon. The drathyrican folds of a young dragon, the organ that generates their magical breath, are crucial to the operation of the spear. The mechanics of the weapon are largely based on an injection spear: when the safety is disengaged and a secondary lever is squeezed, it produces a magical effect like a dragon\u2019s breath from the hollow tip of the spear.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 159,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
        },
        "classes": [
          "uncommon"
        ],
        "edition": "remastered",
        "game-id": "f31704572455b8d77a8bd97c0045fde6",
        "game-obj": "Traits",
        "links": [
          {
            "alt": "Recall Knowledge",
